<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.7">
<l>urukkuṟu naṟuneykoṇ ṭāraḻalil</l>
<l>irukkuṟu mantaṇar cantiyiṉvāy</l>
<l>perukkamo ṭamararka ḷamaranalkum</l>
<l>irukkiṉi liṉṉicai yāṉavaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl,</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who became the sweet music in the Ṛg</l>
<l>With which priests, who are worthy of the Ṛg,</l>
<l>Bestow fragrant ghee which was melted into the full fire</l>
<l>In the evening so that the immortals flourish with abundance,</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
